Welcome to Solaris. This new player guide intends to help you navigate your first tutorial match and help you pick up the basics of the game.

Joining Your First Match:
Before you can jump into offical games, you must first complete a new player game. The new player game will help you understand the basics of Solaris mechanics. 
To join the new player game, navigate to the the main menu. The main menu is the default screen 
when logging in. 
To find games to join, click on the tile titled "Join Game". You should notice two tabs at the top titled "New Games" and "In Progress". 
